<div class='col-sm-12'>
  <h4>{{t "Personalizing Boards" key="personalizing_boards"}}</h4>
</div>
<div class='col-sm-12'>
  <img src={{path "images/board-edit-mode.png"}} alt="" style='width: 100%;' >
</div>
<div class='col-sm-12' style="margin-top: 16px;">
  <ul class="usage-checklist">
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "Use Edit Mode to customize any board — add, remove, or rearrange buttons to fit your communicator's needs." key="extra_home_boards_1"}}</li>
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "Change button labels, images, colors, and actions. You can also record custom audio for any button." key="extra_home_boards_edit"}}</li>
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "Buttons you don't need yet can be hidden and revealed later — so a board that looks busy today may be just right as skills grow." key="extra_home_boards_2"}}</li>
  </ul>
</div>
